{
  "stem": "26609.8",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was not a backyard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Right down there was a door open, but it opens to the other side of the building, to the street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the street was not a straight street you go out, but it was a bit hilly, high up, right down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And so when you opened the door-- the door was open always-- you go out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't locked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But you can-- you could go down to the street there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As I ran with my child quickly down the two stairs-- I was young.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And still, even if I was under-nourished but still strong enough, I kept the child, went-- ran down quickly second floor.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was afraid they would still come, see me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I went out and I thought I'd go out to the other side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't, because if they-- I just felt it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If I go out, they will go after me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They will find me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But as I went out-- we have it here too under the stairs, there is a space, a little space where bins for garbage, there were about two big, like here we have big bins for garbage.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was not much room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I took my child, squeezed myself in before-- behind the garbage bins in the corner.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I think she stopped breathing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She understood.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Even as such a young child, she under-- she stopped breathing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I said, hold on to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Hold on.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I went-- I can see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was like a little triangle open there to go in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But it was so-- not very deep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I couldn't go in and hide very-- be safe there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But I did squeeze myself in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And pushed the two garbage bins in front of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
